As an integral part of the Move2Perform software, the Y Balance Test is a
thoroughly researched, yet easy way to test a person's risk for injury as
well as demonstrate functional symmetry. The Y Balance Test Protocol
was developed through years of research in lower extremity injury
prevention using the Star Excursion Balance Test. This new device and
protocol is highly accurate and can be used for measuring pre and post
rehabilitation performance, improvement after performance enhancement pro.
